Summary: Este es mi primer one-shot espero que les guste es Yuri hard elsanna basado en la pelicula frozen

Title: More Than Just a Number
Author: djupcake
Summary: Elsa is coming off quite possibly the lowest point in her life when she meets Anna. As fate would have it, she's quite possibly the most perfect girl Elsa has ever met and she decides to make them happen. Unfortunately there's one small detail that could put a wrench in her plans. Rated T for swearing and, ahem, suggestive language.

Title: The Monster
Author: djupcake
Summary: The death of her parents and the subsequent reawakening of her powers caused a chain of events in Elsa's life that culminated in the murder of a fellow classmate. Now she and her best friend Anna must say goodbye to their old lives and help Elsa control her powers for good. Modern AU, Helsa pairing in the beginning but it's Elsanna for the most part. Rated M for language mostly.

Title: What Do You Show?
Author: djupcake
Summary: When a new girl moves into Arendelle and shows up at the start of senior year at North Mountain High School, she inevitably changes the lives of four different people, including herself. Modern AU, Rated T for language.

Title: A Sinuous Discovery
Author: VintageBeef
Summary: Anna, a hyperactive redhead is just diagnosed with lupus. Elsa, her bestfriend who secretly loves her, will do everything for her to live to the fullest before she expires. Elsanna.

Title: Melted hearts
Author: ViolentHappyChick
Summary: update will be few and far between but ill try to get as much up as possible! Naruto land's at the Feet of of a certain queen can he melt her heart or will she freeze him out as well? What of the princess?

Title: Dura elección
Author: VirtualSinger
Summary: AU Modern. Anna tenía todo: popularidad, amigas, chicos detrás suya... ¿pero en realidad deseaba todo eso? Con tal de que no volviesen otra vez los fantasmas de su pasado. ¿Pero qué pasará si esos fantasmas vuelven contra otra persona? Elsanna. (No incesto)

Title: Beware the frozen heart (Elsanna) - english
Author: Virtugis
Summary: Elsa and Anna are princesses and sisters, and have just lost their parents in a tragic accident. Elsa, who is 3 years older than Anna, is the future heir to the throne, but her uncontrolled magical powers keep her from fulfilling her royal and family obligations. Can Elsa control her frozen heart after all the time she spent alone, and give herself a chance to rediscover love?

Title: Beware the frozen heart (Elsanna) português
Author: Virtugis
Summary: Elsa e Anna são princesas e irmãs, e acabaram de perder seus pais em um trágico acidente. Elsa, que é 3 anos mais velha que Anna, é a futura herdeira do trono, mas seus poderes mágicos descontrolados a impedem de cumprir com suas obrigações reais e familiares. Poderá Elsa controlar seu coração congelado pelo tempo todo que passou sozinha, e dar uma chance para redescobrir o amor?

Title: Min Søster burdagscake: El pastel de cumpleaños de mi hermana
Author: Vivi.GC
Summary: The cake fic / Forkanna. Traducción. ¿Qué pasará cuando Anna cumpla 18? La puerta sigue separándolas como siempre ¿Será posible que Anna por fin logre llegar a su hermana? Una rebanada de pastel podría lograr la diferencia. Femslash, lemon, temática fuerte.

Title: A red tale
Author: VolksParadox
Summary: Leaving behind the sun-scorched deserts, Anna follows a bounty into the far North. As she ventures into a small town, a fated encounter will test her resolve and her way of life. Some paths, she knows, are colored red. Chapter 3 out of 6 up!

Title: At War's End
Author: VolksParadox
Summary: As a desperate civil war rages on, Elsa's job as a nurse becomes more unbearable by the day. The wounds go deep, and there is no certainty in the future. War AU (loosely based on the Spanish Civil War.)

Title: Broken Paths
Author: VolksParadox
Summary: Each of them had their own road, their own broken life. What will happen when they cross one another? Can their paths be one? / Modern AU, Elsanna, non related. Experimental piece, the first chapter serves as a prologue/introduction. Rated T, will change to M in later chapters. R&R!

Title: Crimson Desires
Author: VolksParadox
Summary: Anna, a young Huntress, agrees to take a job away from home. In a twist of fate, she has a rather unusual encounter with a mysterious Countess; neither of them realizing their paths would never be the same afterwards. Slowburn! Fantasy AU. Update 29/10/2018. Chapter 4 'A Fool's Quest' UP!

Title: Echoes
Author: VolksParadox
Summary: A letter fifteen years too late. Lady Anna's choices are few, and some are perhaps not choices at all. A blue tale. This a story submission for the Elsanna Monthly Contest in the Elsanna Shenanigans Discord. One-shot. 19th Century AU. Reviews are always appreciated!

Title: Elsanna Postcards
Author: VolksParadox
Summary: A series of drabbles and small one-shots. Various AU's, will have warnings at the beginning of each one if necessary. Purely Elsanna. Mostly fluff, some angst mixed. Rated T for now, may change later. Reviews would be most welcome! Newest chapter: Boxing!AU, First Person POV

Title: Every corner of a sin
Author: VolksParadox
Summary: Elsa's actions - equal meassure despair and obsession - escalate as her heart aches for what it cannot have. How far is she willing to go in pursuit of her desires? A black tale. Dark!Elsa, heavy themes of guilt. Unrequited love. Elsanna endgame. Minor character death. Post-Frozen 1, canon-divergent. Multi-chapter. Contains some (bad) poetry.

Title: Through the Storm
Author: VolksParadox
Summary: Anna's reign trembles as the drums of war draw closer. Without her sister's presence, surrounded on all sides, the Queen of Arendelle has to make her hardest choices yet. How much is she willing to sacrifice for her people's safety? Elsanna, slowburn, canon-divergent, war setting. Rated M for mature themes. Chapter IX, 'An Omen of War, is up!

Title: Traum
Author: VolksParadox
Summary: A burning night is all it takes for Elsa to began a slow descent into the depths of Berlin's underground night-life. Inspired by Babylon Berlin (with some Steppenwolf references later one). A golden tale. Roaring 20's AU, set in Berlin. Heavily inspired by Babylon Berlin. Unrelated Elsanna, Shy!Elsa. Multi-chapter.

Title: At the Arendelle Blend
Author: VoluntarilyHere
Summary: Elsanna. Not incest. Modern AU: Anna didn't plan to like anything when she went to the Arendelle Blend. Why would she like that health junk? It's all about the chocolate! She leaves loving more than just the smoothies. She leaves extremely attracted to the worker there. That worker is named Elsa.

Title: The Babies Are Us
Author: vriskastrider
Characters: Anna, Dave S., Elsa, Karkat V.
Summary: dave and karkat help elsanna deliver some babies.

Title: The Grand Adventure
Author: VYCanis
Summary: AU, Pokemon-theme. Anna is an orphan without any past and only hope for the future. Her story begins her Great Adventure...and it starts by wishing on a star the eve of her eighteenth birthday. Rating Tentative, possible unrelated Elsanna later.

Title: The Slipshod Collection
Author: VYCanis

Summary: Modern!AU. Despondent over spending another holiday alone, Anna finds solace in nightly chats with IceQueen13, unaware she's really Elsa Winters, heiress to a bookstore chain. Their online correspondence may develop into something more, even more when Anna visits the shop one day.

Title: Hans' Redemption?
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Set after Frozen & Frozen Fever, Elsa gets a letter from the Southern Isles claiming that Hans had changed and wants to come to Arendelle to try and make amends. However, two mysterious things begin occuring which may cast doubt whether or not Hans truly changed.

Title: Hans' Trial
Author: yugifrozenfan
Characters: Anna, Duke of Weselton, Elsa, Hans
Summary: When we last saw Hans, he was on a ship caged up to be sent back to his kingdom. However, what were the circumstances that led up to that? It left a lot of unanswered questions: Did Hans ever see Elsa again after the thaw? Was he even put on trial by her? It's all here in this short story.

Title: Happy Birthday, Elsa!
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Modern!AU Elsa's birthday is coming up so Anna decides to throw a surprise party for her. Only problem is that Elsa didn't want a party to begin with so will the party be cancelled or will it proceed as planned? Kristoff makes a cameo appearance.

Title: Lifeguard Practice
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Lifeguard!AU To get out of attending summer remedial classes, Anna enrolls in a summer camp design to train and certify lifeguards. Here, she meets Elsa, a very shy girl and tries to develop a friendship with her in the midst of their training (1-3)

Title: Lifeguard Training
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: 2-3. Lifeguard!AU Anna and Elsa's friendship is in full swing and it's time to put those skills to the test. However, will Hans singlehandly destroy the friendship between the girls?

Title: Lifeguarding a Friendship
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: High School!AU Sequel to the Lifeguarding series. Anna and Elsa's friendship is in full swing but when Hans forces Elsa to question Anna's true intentions for befriending her, will their friendship end?

Title: Lifeguarding Waterslides
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: 3-3. The final test has arrived & Anna and Elsa's friendship may become threatened once Anna discovers Elsa's secret. Hans is mentioned

Title: Need Help?
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Republished because the finished product looked more like a Wall of Text. Retail!AU. A mysterious customer turns Anna's otherwise mundane schedule upside down. Acting on a hunch, she uncovers some facts about the customer that may or may not have bad consequences. The queen is mentioned.

Title: Return To The Southern Isles
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Continuing from where Hans' Trial left off, Hans returns from Arendelle and is given another trial to determine his fate. At his brother's request, he testifies at length about his schemes and what is heard may motivate what punishment is selected for him

Title: The Engagement
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Modern AU. Non-related Elsa & Anna fic. Elsa wants to propose marriage to Anna on Christmas Eve but a misunderstanding causes the plan to be derailed as the two eventually discover that marriage isn't about love, it's also about loyalty & honesty.

Title: THe Haunted House
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: It's the annual Halloween carnival in Arendelle. However, when Anna gets trapped in one of the attractions, will she be saved or will she be forced to spend Halloween in a house that's rumored to be haunted? Kai makes a cameo appearance

Title: The Missing Assignment
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: High School!AU. Teacher!Elsa, Student!Anna. Elsa assigns her Resource English class an essay to write on their latest book, but when Anna loses her essay but claims she did it, Elsa decides to test Anna's honesty by giving her one day to recover the paper and turn it in. Featuring Hans, Kristoff & Olaf gets a mention as well.

Title: The Nerd, The Popular Girl and The Bully
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: High School!AU, Nerd!Anna, Popular!Elsa, Bully!Hans. Can nerds intermingle with the popular kids? That's the question that will be answered when Anna, a nerd, meets Elsa, a new student who's immediately inducted into the popular cliche headed by Hans. When she witnesses Hans' torment of Anna, what will she do. Elsanna right at the end.

Title: The Reporter, The Accused and a Tangle of Trouble
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Modern Crime Reporter!AU. A crime has been committed and an arrest was made. However, the person claims she was innocent so investigative newspaper writer Anna Summers is placed on the case. The further she investigates, it comes to light that this is one case that needed to be looked at further. Oaken & The Duke also make appearances

Title: The Wedding
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: The big day for Elsa & Anna has arrived! Sequel to The Engagement & Wedding Plans.

Title: Three Days
Author: yugifrozenfan
Characters: Anna, Elsa, King Agnarr, Queen Iduna
Summary: Canon!Telling Anna Restores Her Memories!AU For one day a year, Anna asks questions as to why Elsa was isolated from her. But when a visitor visits Anna in her sleep one year, It starts a chain of events that may lead to Anna discovering the truth. K for spanking threat.

Title: Trick-Or-Treat!
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Sequel to Costume Shopping, Anna & Elsa deal with Trick-Or-Treaters on Halloween. My contribution to the Frozen halloween fics

Title: Wedding Plans
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Sequel to The Engagement. Anna tries to book the site of her & Elsa's wedding, the park where they met at, but when it turns out that the park has two other events booked, what would she do? And would Elsa accept her wedding theme?

Title: What If?
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Canon-compliant. After the Thaw, Elsa begins wondering what life she and Anna would have led if there was no fear. A conversation with Anna leads Elsa to the trolls, who give her a chance to actually see that life.

Title: What If? The Sequel
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Sequel to What If? After viewing the What If, Anna decides she wants to view it for herself. With the help of Pabbie, Anna takes a trip to see what type of life she and Elsa could have lived. Kristoff & The King & Queen are mentioned and Hans makes a brief appearance.

Title: Where's My Valentine?
Author: yugifrozenfan
Summary: Elsa forgot Valentine's Day, leaving Anna a little sad because it's Valentine's Day. But Elsa has something special planned for Anna to celebrate the occasion. Elsanna Sisterly love. Modern AU

Title: All That You Are
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: Elsa has only just managed to get her life in order after being in a horrific accident years ago. Things get complicated when a new neighbour moves in. Anna is wheelchair-bound from a tragic accident that also killed her parents - the same accident Elsa caused. Guilt-ridden, Elsa tries to hide her past from Anna, not wanting to hurt her again, even as they grow closer... modern!AU

Title: Bribery, Force, and Other Nefarious Tactics
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: Some of the many, many ways Anna tried to get Elsa to open the door, and the one time Anna succeeded. Oneshot.

Title: come back and haunt me (let's go back to the start)
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: 'Anna laughs. In the late afternoon breeze, wisps of auburn hair coming free of her braids and framing her face, she is every bit as beautiful as Elsa has always seen her. In this moment, Elsa realizes she is in love.' Elsa has trouble moving on. Unrelated modern!AU. Rated for sexual content implied and explicit. Oneshot.

Title: Elsa Anna Bare Corona
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: Best friends Elsa and Anna embark on a summer holiday in Corona. Anna gets herself into a host of innuendo-laden situations – all completely misinterpreted by Elsa, of course. Which is bad, because they maybe, sorta, kinda like each other. A fun and naughty romp of epic proportions. Rated for adult themes, implied sexual situations, and language.

Title: Endearingly
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: Anna and Elsa discuss terms of endearments, consider appropriate ones for each other, and conclude they aren't necessary. Elsanna fluff, plain and simple.

Title: Epilogue
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: Hans is not a very nice person, to say the least.

Title: Für Elsa
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: She isn't your precious girl any more. A short piece from the King's point of view.

Title: Revolutionary Girl
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: Elsa needs a new captain of the castle guard. Anna volunteers. Chaos ensues.

Title: Roleplaying
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: Anna loves role playing and taking charge. For a change, Elsa takes over both parts, with unexpected results. PWP. Oneshot. Rated for smutty content and attempted seduction.

Title: Seeing Her
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: "Gone were the early days, in which Anna had lain perfectly still so that Elsa could map out her girlfriend in her mind..." A Café Liégeois-verse Elsanna oneshot. Rated for adult content.

Title: Snowflakes in the Night
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: An AU set in 1830s Paris. Anna, an aspiring opera singer, meets a young woman named Elsa who helps her work towards her dream. But nothing is as clear as it seems, and Elsa is hiding something... and just who is the mysterious Phantom lurking behind everything? Based heavily on Gaston Leroux's original novel, The Phantom of the Opera.

Title: Substitution
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: "Sometimes, when two messed up people meet, it's like they're two puzzle pieces that go together perfectly and fill up the wounds in the other and it's beautiful, but sometimes, that doesn't happen." In which Elsa and Hans build an illusion together, for each other. Elsa/Hans, Elsa/Anna, Hans/Anna. Rated a hard M for explicit sexual content, dub-con, incest, violence, and language.

Title: The Book of Queens
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: She can't touch or be touched. Elsa-centric.

Title: The Nighthawks
Author: yumi michiyo

A connection doesn't necessarily lead to happily ever after if there's too much debris in between. A modern AU in which Elsa and Anna are not related. Rated for strong language, sexual content, and mature themes. Now a series.

Title: The Other Real Thing
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: Elsa can speak nine languages. Elsa can play five musical instruments. But Elsa can't understand her sister Anna, and the way she feels about her. Modern college AU oneshot. Elsa/Anna pairing. Rated for content both existing and implied.

Title: walk you through the maze of the map I'm gazing at
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: "Anna waited impatiently by her laptop, certain the call would come any minute. She had counted the hours it would take Elsa to reach Japan. She'd bought a world map and pasted it to her wall. A blue pin marked Tokyo; a red pin for herself, poked over Lancaster, Philadelphia; an ocean apart." An Elsa/Anna modern!AU in which 365 days are too long to be separated by an ocean.

Title: We Fall Down Inside
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: A collection of unrelated oneshots written for Elsanna!AU week on Tumblr. Rated for sexual content in some, but not all.

Title: Yours For A Song
Author: yumi michiyo
Summary: "What's the difference?" I asked him. "Between the love of your life, and your soulmate?" "One is a choice, and one is not." Elsa wakes up with seven words written on the inside of her left wrist, and her entire life changes. A oneshot of epically cracky proportions. Modern!AU.

Title: Beso
Author: YumiSebby
Summary: Y es que Elsa solo quería un beso, pero Anna se negaba a ello.

Title: elsanna
Author: zachlorthan
Summary: Elsa finds her mother's diary in the midst of a crisis of emotions over her sister. Discovering a family secret, she gives in to her temptations.

Title: Fire and ice

(warning, smut ahead) chapter two fix/extd

Title: 14 de febrero gris
Author: ZafiroKristalino
Summary: -Porque viva te llevaron, viva te devolverán- Elsa en un día de San Valentín luego de la desaparición forzada de su hermana. Drable. Sin parejas.

Summary: Elsa es parte de la mafia, bajo a su cargo tiene a varios jóvenes y sabe que jamás tendrá una vida normal / ¿Sabes porque me uní a esto, a la mafia?/ -No me perdono el que casi te haya matado-/ Porque estar a su lado valía la pena, tanto en el cielo como en el infierno AU Elsaanna (no son hermanas)

Title: El ultraje

Title: La habitación del hospital
Author: ZafiroKristalino
Summary: Abriste la puerta en silencio, deslizando tus dedos por el fino marco mientras te decidías a entrar o a pasar de largo. Un suspiro salió entre tus labios y cerraste los ojos con frustración. En esa habitación aun estaban las voces que tanto te atormentaban. AU actual. Amor fraternal entre hermanas.

Title: Ya nada queda
Author: ZafiroKristalino
Summary: Elsa siente que su vida ya no es importante. Su inmortalidad le habia quitado todo, a Anna, a Kristoff y a todos lo que quería. Sumida en un sueño eterno que ella misma se autoimpone... ¿Pero quien la despierta? 2 EXTRAS SUBIDOS! HISTORIA TERMINADA.

Title: ¿Que hubiera pasado si
Author: ZafiroKristalino
Summary: Hans esta en la carcel luego de haber tratado de matar a la reina Elsa, creyendo que hubiera sido mejor ganar... aunque la victoria podia verse exelente el precio hubiera sido muy caro ¿Que pasaría si alguien se lo hace ver? ¿Que hubiera sido de Hans si ganaba?

Title: Briser la Glace
Author: Zakuro Kagame
Summary: Depuis quand le regard que je portais sur ma sœur avait autant changé ? Son mariage qui approchait m'enfermait peu à peu dans la prison de glace de laquelle je pensais pourtant enfin être sortit. Un amour interdit, des larmes de glaces, et si le cauchemar recommençait...? [One Shot] [Yuri] [Incest]

Title: Ce Secret entre nos Mains Glacées
Author: Zakuro Kagame
Summary: Cela faisait trois mois maintenant qu'Elsa avait quitté le château. Trois mois que je ne pensais plus qu'à elle. Et si elle ne venait à moi, alors j'allais venir à elle. [OneShot] [Yuri] [Incest] [Elsa x Anna]

Title: Frozen Feels
Author: Zakuro Kagame
Summary: Elsa rentre enfin chez elle après plusieurs années d'absence. Elle y retrouve sa soeur, Anna, ou la personne qu'elle avait jusqu'à maintenant le plus cherché à fuir. [Yuri] [OneShot] [Elsa x Anna]

Title: La Seconde Moitié du Miroir
Author: Zakuro Kagame
Summary: L'on dit de moi que je suis froide et détachée. Que je suis telle la moitié d'un miroir brisé duquel l'amour a été arraché. Certains ont tort, d'autres ont raison, d'aucuns ne me connaissent assez pour prétendre comprendre mes émotions. Et lorsque je rencontre enfin l'autre moitié, je sais déjà devoir lui demander pardon. Mes pensées sont péché, que je le veuille ou non. [Futanari]

Title: Que s'envole ce péché, avec les flocons de l'été
Author: Zakuro Kagame
Summary: Le solstice d'été est une journée particulière, c'est aussi l'anniversaire d'Anna. Et pour cette occasion où je décide de rentrer, je ne pensais pas lui partager, le plus terrible de mes péchés. [Yuri] [Incest] [AU] [OneShot] [Elsa x Anna] [Mature Content]

Title: The Guardian
Author: Zaltia
Summary: Anna was good at two things: Eating Chocolate and killing demons. So when the alert came in, she thought nothing about it. She could handle demons. She could handle zombies. She could even handle saving the world. The only thing she couldn't handle was the beautiful angel that she swore to never see again. DemonHunter!Anna, Angel!Elsa and Elsanna Non-Incest.

Title: Storm's Angel
Author: Zaraelyna13
Summary: After Anna watches her parents die before her eyes, she moves with her brother to a town called Arendelle. She starts a new life at a new school, and very quickly runs into a girl named Elsa. (Non-incest Elsanna)

Title: Hopeless
Author: Zassy77
Summary: Anna was in love with a beautiful, introverted platinum blonde. The problem? Well, for starters, that was her best friend. [mAu, unrelated, fluff]

Title: Just A Bit of Your Warmth
Author: Zassy77
Summary: "Would you like to join me?" Elsa blushed, gesturing to the seat across her. Anna tucked her hair behind her ear and grinned. "I'd love to." [mAU Coffee Shop, Unrelated, Oneshot]

Title: Maybe Tonight
Author: Zassy77
Summary: Modern AU. Oneshot. Anna and Elsa have been close friends since they became roommates two years ago during their freshman year of college. Anna never expected, however, that she would have these budding feelings she didn't even realize she had. Or perhaps she was just denying them this entire time. Unrelated Elsanna. Fluff.

Title: Queenie
Author: Zassy77
Summary: Elsa was overworking herself at night, because she was the Queen. But Anna was having none of that. [Canon, Snow Sisters, Fluff, Oneshot]

Title: A Doctor's Romance
Author: Zayad
Summary: Anna is bedridden from a bad fall and lonely from a recent breakup. Elsa is tired, from politics and ruling, but doing the best she can so her sister doesn't have to. But they both agree that there's something about the mysterious resident doctor. Something alluring. Something dangerous. Something attractive. Something new and exciting. Something they both desire for themselves.

Title: Elsanna: The Zebra Cake Fic & Song
Author: ZCakes
Summary: Elsa and Anna show their love with a cake...and a song to help set the mood. Story written by FreezingBella Song written by xXSiRXx

Title: I'm Addicted To You
Author: Zealy
Summary: Elsa is a woman fallen from grace; both addicted to a slew of drugs and abused by her husband, she doesn't see a happy ending in store for herself. Anna is ever chipper and dreams of taking her father's place as the highest paid bartender at the spectacularly renowned Oaken's. As they grow close, will these two very different characters even each other out? Elsanna.

Title: Proud Prince of Arendelle
Author: Zealy
Summary: Elsa was groomed her whole life to rule as a prince, her true gender hidden from all but her closest servants. Following the death of her father, Elsa must choose a wife and eventually figure out how to reveal the truth to her. Elsanna.

Title: The begining
Author: ZeeThePoet
Summary: Elsa starts attending Arendelle High and meets a bubbly, social redhead, will the redhead see past her flaws and past and love her? Trigger warning: Self harm, abuse

Title: The Girl From Nordsgarde
Author: zeitgeistx
Summary: Centuries have passed since the Great War, and magick in the five kingdoms is all but forgotten. Now rumors arise that a witch has killed seven men with her bare hands. Anna, the heir of Arendelle, is tasked to escort the prisoner to trial; and she would not only learn that magick is alive and well, but that there are things worse than losing your life - such as losing your heart.

Title: Reconnecting
Author: Zepherus
Summary: It's her senior year of high school when a person from her past come back...but why is she so different? ELSANNA

Title: Say It Ain't So
Author: ZErO SuBsTaNce
Summary: Anna Sommers life was more than normal, until she got more than she bargained for all in the form Elsa Arendal. Starting her Sophomore year in Arendelle-High she thought she had been clear of her old math teacher, until the day of her family reunion. Join Anna and Elsa as they navigate through school, work, secrets,loss and love will they both survive Arendelle-High? G!P ElsaxAnna

Title: Welcome To The Wonderful Destruction of Anna Anderson's World
Author: ZErO SuBsTaNce
Summary: In a world where creatures of myth exist and live along side humans, join Anna Anderson as she discovers a world much deeper than her own. After finding a suitcase, Anna discovers the secrets within the mysterious case along side it's owner Elsa Menzel. Can Anna manage her cool and attraction to the mysterious Warlock or will secrets within the suitcase destroy them both. G!P

Title: Broken Dreaming
Author: ZoeKar
Summary: !RE-UPLOAD! In a world where an infection transforms its human hosts into cannibalistic monsters, Anna, an 18-year-old girl, finds herself in a tough spot. That's when she meets Elsa, the person she didn't know was missing from her life. Kinda Elsanna, T mostly for violence and mild language.

Title: Guardian Angel
Author: zoepeanut
Summary: Full summary inside. Also a crossover with the Infernal Devices by Cassandra Clare, though it is not necessary to read the books to read this story. Follows the plot of Clockwork Angel using characters from Rise of the Guardians and Frozen. The first chapter contains the summary and background information about the setting, skip over if you simply want to begin reading the story.

Title: A Merciful Heart, A Savage Soul
Author: ZombieSlayerOfTheUnderWorld
Summary: Anna has longed for a child of her own to raise alongside her Elsa, when the royal couple adopts a little boy from Arendelle's Orphanage, they start the road of parenthood. Raising their adopted son will come with some bumps. Political problems, stuck-up councilmen, and the fact that there's more to their adopted son than meets the eye. Elsanna. Icest. T for Violence, Language.

Title: The Birth of A Prince
Author: ZombieSlayerOfTheUnderWorld
Summary: Queen Elsa, and Princess Anna have been married, but something is missing; a new member to the family. When Anna becomes pregnant with a child thanks to some troll magic, their dreams for a child has come true, thus the birth of Prince Xander. A one-shot Prequel for my main fanfic, Son of The Ice Queen.

Title: Truth
Author: ZombieSlayerOfTheUnderWorld
Summary: For the last year he question on why his mothers sometimes call each other 'sister', it would sometimes drive him crazy. Henrik always thought that Anna was his 'father' so to speak, but one night he asks his mothers the question they knew they would have to answer one day, sometimes the truth can be unexpected, but not all truths end in sadness or denial. One-Shot Elsanna fluff

Title: Vengeance
Author: ZombieSlayerOfTheUnderWorld
Summary: After spending the last 17 years in pain, a full grown Edward is fighting his on going war on crime, while he has killed hundreds, if not thousands of criminals, yet he still has nightmares of his tragic past, Edward still hunts for the man name Hans. He will have his Vengeance. Elsanna (only in flashbacks) M for Blood & Gore, Gritty Violence. Based on Iamrotting's Coffee & Arrest.

Title: Vengeance: BORN
Author: ZombieSlayerOfTheUnderWorld
Summary: The memories of Edward are so dear to him, See the precious times he had with his mothers, See the life he had before he became "The Punisher" A one-shot prequel of my Vengeance fanfic, which is based on Iamrotting's Coffee & Arrest. Rated T for dark theme, brief language.

Title: Ever ever after
Author: zphantom
Summary: "I wish, with all my heart's desire, to live happily ever after with my true love." Anna whispered happily then suddenly she felt a strong pushed from her back. And when she opened her eyes, she's falling to the dark oblivion of the well. (Elsanna; non-incest; one-shot)

Title: Harmony Of Two Hearts
Author: Zwischenkraft
Summary: Arendelle was never meant to have only one ruler. Elsa was never the only one with powers, and this strange occurrence was not just a coincidence. The chain of events that lead to these discoveries began when Queen Elsa of Anderelle, also known as the Ice Queen, was calmly walking through her castle when she stumbled upon a shocking scene at the castle's gates.

Title: Spring
Author: Zwischenkraft
Summary: Spring has finally arrived in Arendelle. A lot of things happen in Elsa's head. Literally. Fluff One-shot. Elsanna.

Title: Frozen Love

El tiempo pasa, y Elsa se dará cuenta que el amor, la amistad, y la magia, son cosas muy importantes que cambiaran su vida. [Elsanna] [Sin incesto]

Title: Facets

Title: Argos
Author: 4mation-is-1derful

Title: Sins of Thy Mother

Summary: For her mother and father did love her so little that they would trade her soul for safety. Blood shall pay for blood betrayed. Post movie. Vampire AU.

Title: What am I to You?

Summary: But maybe I didn't want this relationship defined. Maybe I could just leave it at best-friends-that-get-horny-together. Maybe I wasn't in love with her. Maybe she should just drop me like the bad habit this situation is and just be happy with her perfect little boyfriend. Even IF he couldn't satisfy her enough to stop her from coming to me. (Literally...)

Title: No matter what
Author: Abs24
Summary: Il y avait des choses qu'une mère pouvait, et ne pouvait pas faire. Icest, Elsanna.

Title: The Pain of Loss
Author: aguiltyconscience
Summary: One-shot. Sometimes you can't fully appreciate the pain of loss until you experience it for yourself. Elsa learned this lesson when her parents died, but now she is forced to relive it when her sister gets married.

Title: Cry on my Shoulder

Summary: After she catches her husband cheating, Anna moves into her sisters guestroom. (Modern AU)

Title: Let Us Be

Title: Spark

Title: Forever Will Forever Be Ours

Title: Tainted Love

Author: alex-of-macedonia
Summary: The events of Disney's Frozen, as told from Elsa's POV. (Yes, this leads up to incest. If that weirds you out, please don't continue reading.)

Title: Voulez-vous Coucher Avec Moi, Ce Soir?
Author: alex-of-macedonia
Summary: Elsa doesn't have the money to pay for a pizza delivery, so she pays in another way. (Non-incest, modern day.)

Summary: Elsa feels the weight of the crown on her head, sinking into depression after the events of the movie. Is she really the right person to rule? And what about her feelings for her sister...? Elsanna SMUT! Disclaimer: Read at your own peril.

Title: We Know Better
